                    <p>Accreditation is a formal evaluation process through which educational institutions are assessed for quality, consistency, and integrity. For online institutes, it ensures your digital learning environment meets rigorous international benchmarks in curriculum design, faculty competence, student support, data security, and educational outcomes.
